## Description

The Existing ROW layer was created with parcel data received from the county assessor's offices. Each county has different levels of accuracy. If a county did not have a GIS parcel dataset, ERMS was utilized. Strip maps were pulled from ERMS, georectified, and traced over to created the boundary.?
